{"type":"message","id":"c79ef7b6","parentId":"e0e24b02","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:11.670Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-03-19 22:49 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n\n1. 搜索\"企业数字化转型 2026趋势\"相关最新信息\n2. 搜索\"智能安防 2026发展趋势\"最新动态\n3. 搜索\"网络系统集成 2026\"市场动态\n4. 搜索\"IT运维服务 AIOps 2026\"行业趋势\n\n请整理3-5条关键信息，内容要精炼实用，与道简网络业务（企业数字化、网络系统集成、智能安防、IT运维）高度相关。\n\n最后将内容保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md，格式要有条理，便于后续查阅。"}],"timestamp":1773931751667}}
{"type":"message","id":"56e82358","parentId":"c79ef7b6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:32.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要搜索四个主题的最新行业动态，然后整理成精炼实用的信息保存到学习笔记中。让我先搜索这些内容。\n\n由于这是搜索任务，我应该使用 miaoda-web-search skill 来执行搜索。","thinkingSignature":"e80c506144ce838a6d35da1227535719ce7b66ab368be372820c237dd9d0e732"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6wjn8v2vymrn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30881,"totalTokens":31081,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0000996,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037057199999999996,"total":0.0038404199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931751668}}
{"type":"message","id":"21951a77","parentId":"56e82358","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:32.557Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6wjn8v2vymrn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931772555}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad1954a2","parentId":"21951a77","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:37.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了搜索工具的使用方法。让我并行搜索四个主题：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026趋势\n2. 智能安防 2026发展趋势  \n3. 网络系统集成 2026市场动态\n4. IT运维服务 AIOps 2026行业趋势","thinkingSignature":"1ce4431b837b15a218cff684e2256267d62badac3655cf06bac868a47807b307"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_huiamd0zr63k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026趋势\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_huiamd0zr63k_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026发展趋势\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_huiamd0zr63k_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026市场动态\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_huiamd0zr63k_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 AIOps 2026行业趋势\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":914,"output":210,"cacheRead":30682,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31806,"cost":{"input":0.0002742,"output":0.000252,"cacheRead":0.0009204599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014466599999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931772557}}
